Pricing --

Cloudfront edge locations are global
the cost of data out per edge location will varies
More data transfered out, the lower the cost

-----Classes

you can reduce the numer of edge l;ocations for cost reduction
three price classes
  price class all : all regions : best performance (most money)
  price class 200 : most regions but excludes the most expensive regions
  price class 100 : only the least expensive regions
